description: Great Vibes is a beautifully flowing connecting script. It has cleanly looping ascenders and descenders as well as elegant uppercase forms. Great Vibes is a Unicode typeface that supports languages that use the Latin script and its variants, and could be expanded to support other scripts. To contribute to the project contact Rob Leuschke.
